---
title: Herby Bacon & Mushroom Baked Risotto with Flaked Almonds & Garden Salad
description: This comforting mushroom and bacon risotto becomes rich and full of flavour with sharp grated Parmesan. Add a crisp cucumber
salad and toasted almonds to perfectly round out the meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6620d137d7d86b487f183ff4-0302e275.jpeg
